<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-28 20:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3331 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-INTERNET-NAMES-2TAKES     11-28 1272
