<SLUG> BC-FBC-VIRGINIA-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BLACKSBURG JOURNAL: `HOKIE-MANIA' HELPS RAISE VIRGINIA TECH'S
PROFILE
</HEADLINE>
 (DUPLICATION NOTICE: Also sent in ``s'' category)  
(ART ADV: Map is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(nk) 
 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
