<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-28 21:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3365 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-IDAHO-CROSS-ART-450&AMP;A     11-28 0775
