<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-28 22:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3383 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-FBN-JETS-COLTS-NYT &LR;      11-28 1067
